Tatyana goes through the documents and finds out&nbsp;
that the cosmonaut was placed in a rehabilitation&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:25.280
center first, but the creature emerged the first&nbsp;
night and killed a medical technician. Then they&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:29.440
brought him to the facility and started trying to&nbsp;
separate the man from the creature, though nothing&nbsp;&nbsp;

