has worked thus far. Without the creature inside&nbsp;
of him, the cosmonaut's vital signs drop, but with&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:34.560 --> 00:06:40.240
the creature inside, he has amazing capabilities&nbsp;
of regeneration. When the creature is incubating,&nbsp;&nbsp;

