it takes up very little space inside of Kostya's&nbsp;
body. And outside of the cosmonaut it can reach&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:50.560
up to a meter and a half. Exiting his body,&nbsp;
it releases a toxin that knocks out Kostya&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:55.840
and once it exits, it can stay out for an hour&nbsp;
and 40 to 50 minutes. It's exiting schedule has&nbsp;&nbsp;

