side of the window, she tells them to test his&nbsp;
endocrine system, thinking that if they understand&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:29.760
his hormone levels under stress, they'll be&nbsp;
able to figure out what the creature eats.&nbsp;&nbsp;

