Tatyana comes into his room and apologizes,&nbsp;
explaining why she did what she did in the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:08:45.360 --> 00:08:50.000
session. He tells her that he didn't know about&nbsp;
the boy, that he was informed about his existence&nbsp;&nbsp;

