she notices the way the creature looks at it, so&nbsp;
she asks to go inside the room. The Colonel allows&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:26.880
it, so she is put in a protective suit. She enters&nbsp;
the room and puts the toy down for the creature.&nbsp;&nbsp;

