That night, Tatyana is in her room and the Colonel&nbsp;
comes inside uninvited. She proceeds to explain&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:09:47.520 --> 00:09:51.600
to him what she learned from the incident with&nbsp;
the toy. She thinks that the creature and the&nbsp;&nbsp;

