Later, she goes to talk to Rigel and notices&nbsp;
something wrong with one of the videotapes.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:19.200
He says it's a glitch, but she hits him with&nbsp;
the question about the difference in the hormone&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:23.200
levels of the cosmonaut between day and night.&nbsp;
