thinks he wants a Nobel Prize and offers to&nbsp;
help him get it without her own accolades.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:32.080 --> 00:10:36.080
Tatyana asks for the missing information to be&nbsp;
given to her without the Colonel's knowledge.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:41.840
Rigel hides her in his vehicle and sneaks her into&nbsp;
the restricted part of the facility. Meanwhile,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:41.840 --> 00:10:46.400
Kostya is being given sedatives, knocked out and&nbsp;
then wheeled back into the observational room.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:51.280
Rigel parks the car inside the facility&nbsp;
and gives Tatyana night goggles, telling&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:10:51.280 --> 00:10:56.400
her the battery lasts for only ten minutes. He&nbsp;
leaves the car and a giant cage can be seen,&nbsp;&nbsp;

