They turn the lights out and they all put on night&nbsp;
goggles. The creature has left Kostya's body and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:10.160
it's been guided to the cage. Tatyana sees it&nbsp;
from the car, as it goes toward the prisoner, then&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:10.160 --> 00:11:15.040
jumps it and rips his head off. She makes a sound&nbsp;
and one of the soldiers hears her inside the car.&nbsp;&nbsp;

