block at 1 AM. That night, they give him his&nbsp;
pills, but when they leave he throws them up.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:53.440 --> 00:11:58.480
He crushes up the pills and puts them in his tea.&nbsp;
Then, he leaves his room and chats up the nurse&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:58.480 --> 00:12:03.280
that's guarding him, asking her to come inside&nbsp;
and watch a movie with him. She falls asleep on&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:03.280 --> 00:12:09.760
his shoulder. Kostya takes apart the TV and takes&nbsp;
the magnet out. He meets with Tatyana. Then, he&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:09.760 --> 00:12:14.240
places the magnet on the camera which will create&nbsp;
an error. The guard sees that there's something&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:18.240
wrong and comes down to check the camera, but&nbsp;
when he doesn't find anything he leaves and they&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:23.200
can freely pass in front of it. Kostya and Tatyana&nbsp;
go to the freezer room where he sees the bodies.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:23.760 --> 00:12:28.400
There are scans of his body there also. She&nbsp;
asks him if he can feel the creature inside.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:28.960 --> 00:12:33.040
He says that he is the creature and that he can&nbsp;
remember everything in detail of what it has seen.&nbsp;&nbsp;

