Kostya tells her that if Semiradov knew he would&nbsp;
never let him go. His co-pilot is there too,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:44.160
but he's alive. He begs Tatyana to help him,&nbsp;
by enduring two more weeks in the Institute,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:44.160 --> 00:12:48.880
until a review board from Moscow arrives and he&nbsp;
can be set free. She asks him how he could endure&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:48.880 --> 00:12:53.520
the creature killing people for two more weeks.&nbsp;
But, he asks her what she would've done in his&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:53.520 --> 00:12:59.840
stead. Kill herself? Tatyana answers yes. Kostya&nbsp;
doesn't want to be guilty for feeding the creature&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:59.840 --> 00:13:03.920
people or to die there after all that he's&nbsp;
been through. He wants to live and get his son.&nbsp;

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:08.800
Meanwhile in the orphanage, the child goes to&nbsp;
get a package and the nurse finds it again.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:15.040
It scratches her and she calls it an invalid.
Back at the Institute, Tatyana is returning to her&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:15.040 --> 00:13:19.840
room as two soldiers corner her and take her to&nbsp;
the offices of the Colonel. They argue about the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:23.760
morals of the situation with the creature, with&nbsp;
him firmly believing that he's doing the right&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:23.760 --> 00:13:28.960
thing in the name of peace. Tatyana doesn't think&nbsp;
that human sacrifice is needed, but the Colonel&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:28.960 --> 00:13:33.520
tells her what kind of prisoners the men are. He&nbsp;
suggests they go to the feeding together so that&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:33.520 --> 00:13:38.480
she could see it up close. At the feeding ground,&nbsp;
two prisoners are brought inside the cage and the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:38.480 --> 00:13:43.840
creature is let in. It keeps getting closer to the&nbsp;
men and Tatyana begs the Colonel to stop, saying&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:43.840 --> 00:13:48.800
she'll find another way to feed it. Then she&nbsp;
asks to be let inside the cage with the creature.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:48.800 --> 00:13:53.840
She starts singing the same song she heard Kostya&nbsp;
sing before and the creature calms. Rigel and the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:53.840 --> 00:13:58.320
Colonel watch her do it, as the doctor exclaims&nbsp;
that the creature has adapted, that it can hear&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:13:58.320 --> 00:14:04.000
now. While Tatyana is singing to the creature,&nbsp;
Kostya is seen reacting in his room as well, not&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:09.120
unconscious anymore. One of the prisoners undoes&nbsp;
his restraints and the creature hears him move.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:09.120 --> 00:14:14.720
It attacks him and kills him. After the feeding,&nbsp;
the Colonel asks Tatyana if Kostya can control the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:14.720 --> 00:14:20.480
creature. She tells him that he can't do it yet.&nbsp;
With her help, Semiradov thinks, that eventually&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:20.480 --> 00:14:24.640
they will learn how to control the creature.&nbsp;
He asks her to put their differences aside.&nbsp;

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:30.320
The next day, Tatyana is working in the&nbsp;
room with the co-pilot, when Rigel comes in.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:30.320 --> 00:14:35.520
She starts talking to him in Latin, telling him&nbsp;
to help her and Kostya escape. He doesn't want to,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:35.520 --> 00:14:40.720
but she tells him to man up. Later, Rigel brings&nbsp;
her the sedatives she needed, but asks her not&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:46.000
to tell anyone he helped her. She walks over&nbsp;
to the guard and sedates him. Tatyana asks the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:46.000 --> 00:14:51.600
doctor to help one more time. He comes with her&nbsp;
to get Kostya. When she goes inside his room,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:55.440
she finds him on the floor. She tells him&nbsp;
that the Colonel will do anything to keep&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:59.680
the creature there. Moreover, she's figured&nbsp;
out a way to get the creature out of him,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:14:59.680 --> 00:15:03.280
by injecting him with a combination of&nbsp;
drugs that will mimic a specific disease.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:03.840 --> 00:15:08.080
He doesn't want to do it, afraid that the creature&nbsp;
has adapted and that it will survive out of him.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:08.640 --> 00:15:12.240
Furthermore, he thinks the creature has&nbsp;
saved his life and tells her to run,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:17.520
because it chose him for a reason. It was his&nbsp;
punishment for abandoning his son. She tells him&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:17.520 --> 00:15:22.320
his son's name and age, so he changes his mind and&nbsp;
goes with her. The doctor tells them that there's&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:27.680
a car outside and gives her the keys. Tatyana asks&nbsp;
him to come with them, but he's decided to stay.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:31.680
The two of them leave and Rigel goes to&nbsp;
the Colonel's office to make a call to&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:31.680 --> 00:15:36.800
the authorities and give them information about&nbsp;
the Institute. Simultaneously, another soldier&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:42.000
finds the sedated guard. They check the footage&nbsp;
and see that Tatyana and Kostya are running.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:42.000 --> 00:15:47.280
The Colonel orders a response team to be sent,&nbsp;
to bring back Kostya alive and terminate Tatyana.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:47.280 --> 00:15:52.640
The response team finds and stops them. Back at&nbsp;
the office, Rigel is still on the phone, when&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:52.640 --> 00:15:57.600
someone tries to come inside. He ends the call&nbsp;
the moment the Colonel gets inside the office.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:15:57.600 --> 00:16:02.400
The Colonel kills him. Meanwhile, Tatyana&nbsp;
and Kostya are hiding from the soldiers,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:07.040
when he asks for the syringe with the drugs. She&nbsp;
throws it at him and he shoots the drugs in his&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:07.040 --> 00:16:12.240
heart. The creature leaves his body and faces off&nbsp;
with the soldiers. They shoot at the creature,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:12.240 --> 00:16:16.800
but it starts killing them. Tatyana drags&nbsp;
Kostya to a car and they escape the compound.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:23.040
Eventually, the Colonel goes to face the creature.&nbsp;
He drops a smoke bomb and starts shooting at it.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:23.040 --> 00:16:27.680
They're both hurt, but the Colonel shoots at&nbsp;
it again. At the same time, Kostya coughs up&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:27.680 --> 00:16:33.040
blood in the car. Tatyana realizes that he won't&nbsp;
survive without the creature. He says that they&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:33.040 --> 00:16:37.600
can still escape, but she drags him out of the&nbsp;
car. The Colonel reaches them and asks her if&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:42.560
she changed her mind. She says that they have&nbsp;
become fully symbiotic and can't be separated,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:42.560 --> 00:16:46.960
as the soldiers take the creature out of the&nbsp;
trunk. The Colonel drops the gun she was holding&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:46.960 --> 00:16:52.080
and the soldiers open the creature's enclosure.&nbsp;
The Colonel incapacitates her, but Kostya manages&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:52.080 --> 00:16:56.960
to control the creature and it kills the soldiers.&nbsp;
He goes after the Colonel next and kills him too.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:16:57.520 --> 00:17:02.400
Tatyana goes to check if Kostya is still alive&nbsp;
as the creature crawls to them. It doesn't kill&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:07.120
her and gets back into Kostya's body. She tells&nbsp;
him that she can separate them if she can get him&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:07.120 --> 00:17:12.960
to Moscow. Suddenly, Kostya kills himself, as the&nbsp;
authorities Rigel called for arrive at the scene.&nbsp;

00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:17.760
Tatyana is going to Rostov, where&nbsp;
the orphanage with Kostya's son is.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:22.480
In a flashback, the kid comes back for the&nbsp;
package. The nurse finally acknowledges its&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:22.480 --> 00:17:27.600
persistence and gives it the package. It&nbsp;
opens it to find sneakers inside. Tatyana&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:27.600 --> 00:17:32.000
walks inside the orphanage and tells the guard at&nbsp;
reception that she's there to adopt Kostya's son.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:32.640 --> 00:17:37.680
Meanwhile, the child is putting on the sneakers&nbsp;
and stands up from its wheelchair. The nurse says&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:37.680 --> 00:17:42.160
that everything will be alright and the child&nbsp;
turns and tells her that its name is Tatyana.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:17:42.160 --> 00:17:47.600
In the present, she's waiting outside for the boy.&nbsp;
He comes out and she greets him. They embrace.

